text: The Liuchiu Yu Lighthouse or White Lighthouse () is a lighthouse in Liuqiu Township, Pingtung County, Taiwan. ==Architecture== The lighthouse is a white round tower standing in height. ==See also== * List of tourist attractions in Taiwan * List of lighthouses in Taiwan ==References== Category:1929 establishments in Taiwan Category:Lighthouses completed in 1929 Category:Lighthouses in Pingtung County
title: Liuchiu Yu Lighthouse
